Here's the corrected PlantUML component diagram for the annashres_CustomerBot system focusing on data flow:

```plantuml
@startuml annashres_CustomerBot

component "Azure Bot Service" {
    component "Bot Framework" {
        [bot.js] as bot
        [botdisplay.js] as botdisplay
    }
}

component "Channels" {
    [Webchat]
    [Emulator]
    [Email]
}

component "Data Storage" {
    [Azure SQL Database] as sql_db
    [Power BI Dashboard] as powerbi
}

component "Authentication" {
    [Pin-Based Auth]
}

bot --> sql_db : "Stores/retrieves\nconversation data"
bot --> powerbi : "Sends analytics data"
bot --> Pin-Based_Auth : "Verifies user identity"

botdisplay --> Webchat : "Renders\nAdaptive Cards"
botdisplay --> Emulator : "Renders\nAdaptive Cards"
botdisplay --> Email : "Renders\nMarkdown"

bot --> botdisplay : "Requests\nUI rendering"

Webchat --> bot : "User input"
Emulator --> bot : "User input"
Email --> bot : "Parsed email input"

note right of bot
Handles conversation flow,
database operations,
and NLP processing
end note

note right of botdisplay
Manages presentation logic,
Adaptive Cards rendering,
and channel-specific formatting
end note

@enduml
```